description:
it's appropriate that my first yelp review be of farley's. i go there everyday and i love it. i have no idea what makes their lattes so amazingly good, but sometimes i have to sit down when i take the first sip to handle it. 

some of the baristas (are they called that outside starbucks?) can have an attitude. you have to *earn* your friendly hello by proving you are a farley's regular. but i kinda like that. 

while they have a fantastic selection of magazines, sadly, the copies of businessweek are always several weeks old :(
